name: Biden
summary: Recent polls are showing setbacks for Joe Biden's presidential ambitions. An AP-NORC poll indicates that a majority of Americans believe he should withdraw from the race. Tester, have publicly expressed concerns about Biden's viability as a candidate. A CBS News poll suggests that Trump has widened his national lead over Biden. There are reports that House Speaker Pelosi has shared internal polling with Biden, indicating that he may not be able to win and could jeopardize the Democratic majority in the House. Amidst these challenges, there are signs that some top Democrats believe Biden will ultimately decide not to seek another term.

name: Esta TerBlanche
summary: Esta TerBlanche, an actress best known for her role as Gillian Andrassy on the soap opera "All My Children," has passed away at the age of 51. Her death was reported by several entertainment news outlets, including TMZ, Deadline, Variety, TheWrap, USA TODAY, E! NEWS, New York Post, PEOPLE, Page Six, and Entertainment Weekly. No further details about her passing have been released at this time.

name: USA vs South Sudan
summary: In a pre-Olympic exhibition game, Team USA narrowly escaped an upset against South Sudan. Led by LeBron James' clutch performance in the final minutes, the Americans ultimately emerged victorious 101-100. James' game-winning shot with eight seconds remaining proved crucial in avoiding a shocking defeat. The match, which marked the opening of the USA Basketball Showcase in London, showcased a thrilling contest between the two teams. Despite trailing by 14 points at one point, Team USA's resilience and James' leadership ultimately prevailed.

name: USA Basketball
summary: The United States men's basketball team has had a successful run in the lead-up to the 2024 Paris Olympics. They recently held an exhibition game against Australia, showcasing their skills and teamwork. In another game against Serbia, Stephen Curry led the team to a dominant victory, scoring 24 points. Despite facing unique pressures associated with representing the United States, the team remains determined to perform well at the Olympics. The upcoming WNBA All-Star Game will feature a special showdown between the USA and WNBA teams. The match will provide a glimpse of the talent and athleticism of women's basketball. Team USA men's basketball has also had a successful showing, narrowly defeating South Sudan in a tune-up game for the 2024 Olympics.
